import { useState } from "react"; import { Modal, Row, Col, Form, Table } from 'react-bootstrap' import {Link} from 'react-router-dom' import { API } from "../config/api"; import Swal from "sweetalert2"; export default function ModalGiveResponse({item}) { let navigate = useNavigate() const [form, setForm] = useState({ giveResponse: '', consultationLink: '', }) const handleChange = (e) => { setForm({ ...form, [e.target.name] : e.target.value, }); } const handleSubmit = useMutation(async (e) => { try { e.preventDefault() // Store data with FormData as object const formData = new FormData() formData.set('giveResponse', form.giveResponse) formData.set('consultationLink', form.consultationLink) const _ = await API.post('/response/' + item.ID) Swal.fire({ title: 'Success!', text: 'Response berhasil dibuat', icon: 'success', confirmButtonText: 'Kembali' }) navigate('/reservasi-data') } catch (e) { console.log("add Response failed : ", e); Swal.fire({ title: 'Error!', text: 'Response gagal dibuat', icon: 'error', confirmButtonText: 'Kembali' }) } }) const [show, setShow] = useState(false); return ( <> setShow(false)} aria-labelledby="example-modal-sizes-title-lg" >
{item.Subject}
{item.Description}
Date of complaint
